SELECTED SCENES OF THE TWA STARSTREAM* JET
Here are the scenes practically impossible for you to photograph. Never before
available in such superb 8 mm. color quality and clarity.
TW-850 • STARSTREAM JETS • 18 SCENES
The TWA New York Flight Center ...servicing and
loading plane at Jetway...passengers boarding...
TWA StarStream Jet taxiing out onto runway... the
actual take-off (1. to r.) ...jet flying serenely above
the clouds... landing... take-off again.. air-to-air
in-flight
scenes against blue sky
and
fluffy white
clouds...cockpit— pilot at controls...movies in flight
...cabin interior with hostess... view through cabin
window...landing...taxiing in...passengers deplaning.
Obviously, many of these scenes could be obtained only by aerial photographers,
shooting
from another plane. This TWA 100 foot Stock Film Reel has
18 different scenes and runs for over five minutes. In addition to magnificent
color fidelity, these scenes are especially prepared so they can be spliced into
your own original travel films without loss of focus because the emulsions are
on the same side. Edit these scenes into your own movies — create a more pro-
fessional production with these dramatic in-flight and exterior shots. Order the
TWA Stock Film Reel listed on the order blank inside. Available now at a
Special Low Price, $7.95. *TWA StarStream is a service mark owned exclusively by Trans World Airlines, Inc.
